 "html": "<p>Die ribbetjie moet stadig en tydsaam gaar gemaak word oor rustige kole.  Daar moet meer as een glas wyn gedrink word.  As jy die ribbetjie aflaai moet dit geskroei wees  &#8211; amper of dit gebrand het.  Daar tussen-in sit die diep lekkerte.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lmsrib-op-braai-064.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1249\" alt=\"lmsrib op braai 064\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lmsrib-op-braai-064-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>BENODIG:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>2 stukkies lams of skaaprib<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lmsrib-op-braai-002.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1237\" alt=\"lmsrib op braai 002\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lmsrib-op-braai-002-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>2 takkies vars roosmaryn</li>\n<li>6 knoffelhuisies<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lmsrib-op-braai-012.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1240\" alt=\"lmsrib op braai 012\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lmsrib-op-braai-012-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>250 ml tamatiesous</li>\n<li>125 ml worcestersous</li>\n<li>125 ml chutney</li>\n<li>60 ml asyn</li>\n<li>60 ml bruinsuiker</li>\n<li>ruim koljander</li>\n<li>sout en peper<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lmsrib-op-braai-006.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1238\" alt=\"lmsrib op braai 006\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lmsrib-op-braai-006-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>NOU:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>geur die vleis ruim met koljander, sout en peper<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lmsrib-op-braai-007.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1239\" alt=\"lmsrib op braai 007\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lmsrib-op-braai-007-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>sny die roosmaryn en knoffel fyn en gooi in n bakkie<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lmsrib-op-braai-013.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1241\" alt=\"lmsrib op braai 013\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lmsrib-op-braai-013-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>gooi die res van die bestandele bymekaar<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lmsrib-op-braai-017.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1242\" alt=\"lmsrib op braai 017\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lmsrib-op-braai-017-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a>en smeer die vleis lekker in<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lmsrib-op-braai-019.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1243\" alt=\"lmsrib op braai 019\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lmsrib-op-braai-019-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>laat dit marineer in die yskas vir minstens 60 minute</li>\n<li>maak jou kole en braai stadig, nie te laag nie.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lmsrib-op-braai-047.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1245\" alt=\"lmsrib op braai 047\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lmsrib-op-braai-047-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>al lyk dit of dit brand, skrik nie, dis die lekkerte<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lmsrib-op-braai-050.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1246\" alt=\"lmsrib op braai 050\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lmsrib-op-braai-050-768x1024.jpg\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>Eet die vleis met die tradisionele braaibroodjie en tamatieslaai.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lmsrib-op-braai-060.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1247\" alt=\"lmsrib op braai 060\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lmsrib-op-braai-060-768x1024.jpg\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
